data.description: 3.5% INTEREST RATE AVAILABLE to qualified buyers on the existing ASSUMABLE FHA MORTGAGE!!! Why wait months for a new build, when you can get more bang for your buck and buy this like-new home with all the best features and finishings ALREADY INCLUDED in the price AND get a better rate than what builder buy-downs can offer? Welcome home to the HAWTHORNE model which is a contemporary Florida home, freshly built by DR HORTON in 2021. This beauty is MOVE-IN READY, and it comes with a ton of UPGRADES including CEILING FANS, window blinds, light fixtures, and some convenient SMART FEATURES, too! This home is ENERGY STAR CERTIFIED, and the floor plan is a spacious and inviting SINGLE STORY layout that seamlessly blends functionality and comfort. The front door opens to an EXTRA WIDE BREEZEWAY that leads into the OPEN CONCEPT living area that is warm and welcoming. There is plenty of natural light and a wide-angle view of the backyard through the sliding doors. The kitchen is decked out with stylish BIANCO ANTICO GRANITE counters, undermount sink, 42” white cabinets with gold finish hardware and gold sink fixture to match. Any chef would agree that there is ample counter space and storage including a nice WALK-IN PANTRY. You’ll make some great memories gathering with family and friends around the huge ISLAND with a built-in BREAKFAST BAR, and there is a separate dining area for more formal occasions, as well. For added privacy, the Master Bedroom is conveniently situated at the back of the home, providing a peaceful sanctuary. It features TWO WALK-IN CLOSETS and a beautiful en suite bathroom that contains a DUAL SINK vanity with granite counters, a GARDEN SOAKING TUB, separate shower, and a private WATER CLOSET. The home accommodates three additional spacious bedrooms, one of which serves as a MINI-MASTER SUITE with its own WALK-IN CLOSET and full bathroom. You’ll enjoy plenty of storage throughout this home, too, including a HUGE LINEN CLOSET inside of the spacious laundry room. This amazing home is also situated on a lot that has a pond view behind it, so it’ll always provide a great Florida view from the REAR COVERED PATIO. This gorgeous home is located in the highly sought-after community of SILVERADO in Zephyrhills. This community offers an amenity center complete with a shaded playground, RESORT STYLE POOL, and covered or open seating for relaxing in your favorite way. All of this is offered at an AMAZING PRICE, so skip the haggling, the hassle, and the hidden costs of dealing directly with a builder and make this like-new home yours RIGHT AWAY!  ***The monthly HOA of $60 includes Spectrum Cable/Internet. The 2023 PROPERTY TAX BILL OF $9,564.06 includes annual property taxes of $6,181.05 and the annual CDD of $3,283. Buyers may receive significant tax savings, if they have SOH portability benefits from their prior homestead.***
